divs: sighting detailsnote: entered by field investigator picture to be uploaded. my husband and i pulled over to take a picture of the sun\trees. used i-phone. after looking at picture later that day i noticed a whitish object just above the trees. i did not notice anything when i took the photo. witness felt perplexed when she stopped to take a random picture, and even more so when she looked at it and saw the object. she felt a surge of energy while taking picture. not sure if there was sound, no heat, no smell. was a clear day, no clouds, minimal breeze from the sea.
Summary: Took a picture on I-Phone of trees/sun. Looking at it later noticed a large white object in photo.
